headline: Raymond James Financial (NYSE:RJF) Declares Dividends on Preferred and Common Shares
summary: Raymond James Financial (NYSE:RJF) announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.50 per share on common stock, set for July, which potentially bolstered investor sentiment, contributing to a 13% increase in share price over the last month. Alongside, the company's solid second-quarter earnings report indicating improved revenue and net income over the previous year further supported the upward trajectory.
